data.description: Popular "Eldorado" location in beautiful Menifee. This 4 bedroom with a large loft has 1 bedroom and full bath downstairs. Nice size kitchen with granite counters, maple cabinetry and stainless steel appliances all overlooking the spacious family room with a cozy fireplace. Large backyard with an alumawood patio cover and above ground pool and above ground spa with plenty of space left over. There's a 3 car tandem garage with epoxy floors. Upstairs laundry and a large loft that can easily be converted into a 5th bedroom. The master suite has a separate tub/shower and big walk-in closet. Walking distance to the community park. Priced to sell!
